  <h1 class="gd-h1">Heliskiing in Greenland</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">Greenland is heliskiing's ultimate frontier: vast untouched glaciers, couloirs and ridgelines dropping toward icebergs and the open Arctic sea, reached by boat or basecamp in a short late season. This guide covers the terrain, the expeditionary style, the April to May window and how to plan it, before pointing you towards our <a href="/packages">packages</a> and the accessible Arctic of <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
</div></section>
